某电商平台后端服务中，存在计算订单可退款金额的核心方法`calcRefundableAmount`，需严格遵守以下业务规则与约束：
1. 所有入参均为`Long`类型，单位为「分」，若任意入参为`null`，直接抛出`NullPointerException`；
2. 订单总金额`orderTotal`必须为正整数（>0），否则抛出带错误码`ORDER_TOTAL_INVALID`的`IllegalArgumentException`；
3. 已使用优惠券金额`couponUsed`必须为非负整数，且≤`orderTotal`，否则抛出带错误码`COUPON_USED_INVALID`的`IllegalArgumentException`；
4. 已发货商品不可退款金额`shippedNonRefund`必须为非负整数，且≤`orderTotal - couponUsed`，否则抛出带错误码`SHIPPED_NON_REFUND_INVALID`的`IllegalArgumentException`；
5. 已申请退款金额`appliedRefund`必须为非负整数，且≤`orderTotal - couponUsed - shippedNonRefund`，否则抛出带错误码`APPLIED_REFUND_INVALID`的`IllegalArgumentException`；
6. 最终可退款金额 = `orderTotal - couponUsed - shippedNonRefund - appliedRefund`，若计算结果<0则返回0，否则返回计算结果。

当前实现的Java代码如下（存在边界条件与异常处理的微妙错误，需定位所有错误点并完成后续要求）：
```java
public Long calcRefundableAmount(Long orderTotal, Long couponUsed, Long shippedNonRefund, Long appliedRefund) {
    // 校验orderTotal
    if (orderTotal == null || orderTotal <= 0) {
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("ORDER_TOTAL_INVALID");
    }
    // 校验couponUsed
    if (couponUsed == null || couponUsed < 0 || couponUsed > orderTotal) {
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("COUPON_USED_INVALID");
    }
    // 校验shippedNonRefund
    if (shippedNonRefund == null || shippedNonRefund < 0 || shippedNonRefund > orderTotal - couponUsed) {
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("SHIPPED_NON_REFUND_INVALID");
    }
    // 校验appliedRefund
    if (appliedRefund == null || appliedRefund < 0 || appliedRefund > orderTotal - couponUsed - shippedNonRefund) {
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("APPLIED_REFUND_INVALID");
    }
    Long result = orderTotal - couponUsed - shippedNonRefund - appliedRefund;
    return result < 0 ? 0L : result;
}
```
